description: Subaru was rescued from from a burning airport by Nanoha four years prior. This inicident inspired Subaru to join the armed forces with aspirations of becoming a powerful mage. By chance she was transfered into Mobile Section Six`s Stars squad commanded by the very same person who rescued her. On the field, she is equipped with the rollerblade-like intelligent device Mach Caliber and the armed device Revolver Knuckle.
name: Subaru Nakajima
